query:
ALTER TABLE workout_logs 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS sessionId INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS trainingDate DATE,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS dayName VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS startTime VARCHAR(5),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS endTime VARCHAR(5),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS totalDuration INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS totalSets INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS totalReps INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS totalVolume DECIMAL(10,2) DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS totalExercises INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS feeling ENUM('great', 'good', 'normal', 'tired', 'exhausted'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS status ENUM('in_progress', 'completed', 'cancelled') DEFAULT 'in_progress',
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS completedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS hasPendingSuggestions BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE;
